org.openjdk.tools.javac.jvm

类 JNIWriter

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.openjdk.tools.javac.jvm.JNIWriter

  • public class JNIWriter
extends Object
    This class provides operations to write native header files for classes.

    This is NOT part of any supported API. If you write code that depends on this, you do so at your own risk. This code and its internal interfaces are subject to change or deletion without notice.

      boolean multiModuleMode
      If true, class files will be written in module-specific subdirectories of the NATIVE_HEADER_OUTPUT location.
